res-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x6493;</span></a><a href="/whv/憢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x61A2;</span></a><a href="/whv/徺"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5FBA;</span></a><a href="/whv/嶢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5DA2;</span></a><a href="/whv/嬈"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5B08;</span></a><a href="/whv/墝"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x589D;</span></a><a href="/whv/嘵"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5635;</span></a><a href="/whv/僥"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x50E5;</span></a><a href="/whv/堯"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x582F;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
