%81n-Kh%E1%BB%9Fi/author-Lmk1srGEtNuIi0hYAVvAPA">Tiền Khởi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Lan-Anh-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hu%E1%BB%87-Anh/T%C3%B4-%C4%91%C3%A0i-tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-03/poem-vQ0SaQgVQFVorBJNoqac_w">Tô đài trúc chi từ kỳ 03 - 蘇台竹枝詞其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Lan-Anh-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hu%E1%BB%87-Anh/author--wNQkHt_M9ki486cqk9mrA">Tiết Lan Anh, Tiết Huệ Anh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%B9ng-ca-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Nghi%C3%AAm-nh%E1%BB%8B-bi%E1%BB%87t-gi%C3%A1/poem-5aK2JlX-k3k02Onr4xn2SQ">Tương phùng ca, tặng Nghiêm nhị biệt giá - 相逢歌贈嚴二別駕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
